Package: libsquash-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libsquash (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: compression abstraction library (development files)
 Squash provides a single API to access many compression libraries, allowing
 applications a great deal of flexibility in choosing compression algorithms,
 including the option to pass that choice along to the user.
 .
 This package contains the header files.

Package: libsquash0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: compression abstraction library
 Squash provides a single API to access many compression libraries, allowing
 applications a great deal of flexibility in choosing compression algorithms,
 including the option to pass that choice along to the user.
